Package: gboggle
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Recommends: wamerican | wbritish | wordlist
Description: Internationalized version of the classic boggle game
 GBoggle is a classic boggle game for GTK+ platform. It supports 
 internationalization of dictionaries and alphabets (currently English and
 Hungarian are supported). Visual feedback is provided on the board for input
 words and shows missed words at the end of the game.
